      <title>PG&E 与 KKR 就出售 Power Unit 少数股权进行谈判</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/pg-e-in-talks-with-kkr-to-sell-minority-stake-in-power-business</link>
      <description><![CDATA[PG&amp;E Corp. 正在洽谈将其发电业务的少数股权出售给投资公司 KKR &amp; Company。 Co.，交易监管机构已表示他们不打算支持。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/pg-e-in-talks-with-kkr-to-sell-minority-stake-in-power-business</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 21:04:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>沃伦·巴菲特的 PacifiCorp 现在面临 300 亿美元的火灾索赔要求</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-29/buffett-s-pacificorp-now-faces-30-billion-fire-claim-demand</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伯克希尔哈撒韦公司 (Berkshire Hathaway Inc.) 旗下的 PacifiCorp 目前面临 2020 年俄勒冈州劳动节野火受害者索要 300 亿美元的索赔，这是对美国西部最大电网运营商的法律攻击升级。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-29/buffett-s-pacificorp-now-faces-30-billion-fire-claim-demand</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 29 Apr 2024 21:54:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
